	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iam ante quoque scripsi<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="p8459" cert="high">Werdmüllers</persName> letzter Brief an <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullinger</persName>, der noch erhalten ist, datiert vom 23. Mai 1539; s. <bibl>HBBW</bibl> IX, <ref target="file11318">Nr. 1275</ref>.</note>, pater inprimis observande, de statu rerum mearum.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae num acceperis, ignoro.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nullas enim e patria literas accepi, ex quo <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basilea</placeName><note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l28" cert="high">Basilea</placeName> <hi>korrigiert aus</hi> <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName>.</note> discessi<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="p8459" cert="high">Werdmüller</persName> hatte <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basel</placeName> zu Ende des Jahres 1539 verlassen; vgl. unten <ref target="file11429">Nr. 1386</ref>, Anm.1.</note>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iterum igitur scribo et vehementer oro, ne in aliam partem, atque ego feci, abitum meum interpretari velitis, qui paratus sum et tibi et omnibus, quos deus mihi praefecit<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>Vor</hi> praefecit <hi>gestrichenes</hi> praeposuit.</note>, per omnia morem gerere.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam quod ab hoc, ubi nunc sum, loco solum absterrebat, re ipsa<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c"><hi>in der Vorlage</hi> reipsa.</note> comperio sine periculo esse.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vivo alioqui satis foeliciter laboreque victum mihi paro publice praelegendo.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque deo immortali gratias ago, qui me nusquam destitutum esse patiatur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis, obsecro, d. <persName ref="p7077" cert="high">Iacobum Ammanium</persName> et reliquos praeceptores in perpetuum colendos.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">20. februarii 1540.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Parrisiis</placeName>, prope collegium Plessiacum in vico Iacobęo<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Das alte "Collège du Plessis", von Geoffroi du Plessis 1317/1323 gegründet, stand an der Rue Saint-Jacques; vgl. M. <hi>Barroux,</hi> Art. Plessis (Collège du), in: La Grande Encyclopédie, Bd. 26, <placeName ref="l378" cert="high">Paris</placeName> [s. d.], S. 1090.</note>, ubi tres pisces dependent.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8459" cert="high">Otho Werdmüllerus</persName>, tuus filius obsequentissimus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Celeberrimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrico Bullingero</persName>, domino et patri suo in perpetuum colendo.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zürich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
